07:19.569 --> 07:23.239
♪ See the money,
wanna stay for your meal ♪

07:23.273 --> 07:26.575
♪ Get another piece of pie
for your wife ♪

07:26.610 --> 07:29.745
♪ Everybody wanna know
how it feel ♪

07:29.779 --> 07:33.515
♪ Everybody wanna see
what it's like ♪

07:33.550 --> 07:36.418
♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,
I don't mind ♪

07:36.453 --> 07:40.422
♪ Me and Missy is
so busy, busy making money ♪

07:40.457 --> 07:41.890
♪ All right ♪

07:41.925 --> 07:47.429
♪ All step back,
I'm 'bout to dance ♪

07:47.464 --> 07:48.531
♪ The greenback boogie ♪

07:48.532 --> 07:53.532
